quran[118]{c,v,t}:
  23,1,"Toto Abasuubili bamala okhubura."
  23,2,"Balia abehotselesinjia mukhulaama (mukhuswaliya) khwabu."
  23,3,"Nende balia aberetsanga ehale nende amakhuwa kabulamwo oluchendo."
  23,4,"Nende balia abarusinjia eshihanwa shia Izakaa."
  23,5,"Nende balia abalindanga ebiekenyi biabu."
  23,6,"Halali khubakhasi babu nohomba balia abemikhono chiabu emilunji chiatila, kho abo shibafunanibwa tawe."
  23,7,"Ne ulia wenya kalali kano tawe, abo nibo babura eshichelo."
  23,8,"Nende balia bahenganga ebiabachelekhwa nende indakano yabu."
  23,9,"Nende balia balumiililanga khumalaamo kabu (iswala)."
  23,10,"Abo nibo balichelama (balibukula)."
  23,11,"Nibo abalichelama Firdaus mwikulu, balimenyamwo tsinyanga tsioosi."
  23,12,"Ne toto khwaloonga Omundu okhurulana nende liloba."
  23,13,"Mana nikhumulonga okhurulana nende amatsi kolwibulo, akarebwa habundu ehenzefu muno."
  23,14,"Mana nikhukalonga okhuba lilika, mana nikhulonga lilika okhuba eshitonye shieyinyama, mana nikhulonga eshitonye shieyinyama okhubamwo ebikumba, mana nikhufunikha ebikumba inyama, mana nikhumukhola okhuba eshilonje shindi. Ni woluyali muno Nyasaye, Omulonji omulayi muno umalayo."
  23,15,"Mana toto enywe olunyuma lwa ako mulifwa."
  23,16,"Mana toto enywe mulilamusibwa inyanga yeyindukho."
  23,17,"Ne toto khwalonga hekulu wenyu tsinjila saba, ne efwe shikhwali abebilila eshilonje shiosishiosi tawe."
  23,18,"Ne khweshia amatsi kayelele okhurula mwikulu mana nikhukawotselesia khwiloba, ne toto efwe khuli nende obunyali bwokhukayiniaho."
  23,19,"Khu amatsi ako nikhubamesilia emikunda chietsitende nende tsizabibu, munyoolangamwo ebiamo ebinji biamulitsanga."
  23,20,"Nende omusala kurulanga khushikulu shia Sinai, kurusinjia amafura okhuba kokhutongwamwo khubalia."
  23,21,"Ne toto mutsisolo mulimwo nende ameeko, khubanywesinjia khubilia bili mutsinda tsiatsio, ne munyoolangamwo obukhoonyi obunji, ne etsindimwo mutsiliitsanga."
  23,22,"Ne hekulu watsio nende khubwaro muchingungwa."
  23,23,"Ne toto khwaruma Nuhu khubandu bebe, mana naboola mbu; “Enywe Abandu banje, laame Nyasaye. Mubula nyasaye wundi owulali Ye tawe, kho shimuritsangakhwo tawe?"""
  23,24,"Mana omukanda kwabakhongo babakhayi mubandu bebe nikuboola mbu; “Uno shini shiosishiosi tawe halali omundu shinga enywe, yenyanga okhwikhola omulayi khwinywe, ne Nyasaye yenyanga (okhubechesia), yakheshiye Abamalaika. Efwe shikhwawulilakhwo kano khubakofu befu bakhale tawe."
  23,25,"Uno shali shiosishiosi tawe halali ni Omundu uli nende lilalu. Mumulindilile butswa hatiti."""
  23,26,"(Nuhu) naboola mbu; “Nyasaye wanje Omulesi, habina esye, toto bano bamalile okhukhaya.”"
  23,27,"Mana nikhumufimbulila mbu; “Kasia eliaro imbeli wetsimoni tsiefu nende obufimbuli bwefu. Kho olwa likhuwa liefu liliula, mana lichiko libitikhe amatsi, awo injisiamwo okhurula mubuli tsimbia bibili bibili, nende Abandu bobo, halali ulia owelikhuwa lilie liamala okhubura (mbu oyo yakhasishe). Kho olaboola ninasi khubalia abakholela obubii emioyo chiabu tawe. Toto abo balasishibwa.”"
  23,28,"Ne olwa witsa okhunyoola obwihotselefu ewe nende abali halala ninawe mubwaro obo, boola mbu; “Okhwitsomibwa khwoosi nikhwa Nyasaye owakhuhabina efwe okhurulana nende Abandu ababii.”"
  23,29,"Ne boola mbu; “Nyasaye wanje, nzishia habundu wetsimbabaasi, ne toto ewe newe omulayi muno wokhwishia.”"
  23,30,"Toto mukano kalimwo ameeko amakhongo, ne toto efwe khwali bokhubakholela amatemo."
  23,31,"Mana nikhurera inyuma wabu Abandu bandi."
  23,32,"Mana nikhubarumila Abarumwa okhurula mubo okhubaboolela mbu; “Laame Nyasaye, mubula nyasaye wundi owulali Ye tawe, shimuritsangakhwo tawe?”"
  23,33,"Mana omukanda kwabakhongo babakhayi mubandu bebe okwakhaya nikuyingasia omukhung’ano kweyindukho, mana nikhubayindiasia khubulamu bwo khushialo, baboola mbu; “Uno shini shiosishiosi tawe halali ni Omundu shinga enywe, alitsanga ebia mulitsanga, ne anywetsanga ebia munywetsanga."
  23,34,"Ne nimuloonda Omundu butswa shinga enywe, mulaba musishile."
  23,35,"Koo, abalakanga mbu nimumalile okhufwa mwaba liloba nende ebikumba, mbu mulilamusibwa?"
  23,36,"Shikanyalikhana tawe, shikanyalikhana tawe, akamulakungwa ako."
  23,37,"Toto buno ni obulamu bwokhushialo, khufwitsanga nekhumenyanga, ne efwe shikhulilamusibwa tawe."""
  23,38,"Toto uno ni Omundu wachishila sa Nyasaye obubeyi, ne efwe shikhumusuubila tawe."
  23,39,"Yaboola mbu; “Nyasaye wanje Omulesi, habina esye khulwa bayingasiyie."""
  23,40,"Naboola mbu: “Ahambi hano betsa okhwiyitsulisia.”"
  23,41,"Mana oluyoka nilubabukula khubwatoto mana nikhubakhola shinga amakokha kabengabenganga khumatsi, nibakorera ehale Abandu ababii."
  23,42,"Mana nikhurera inyuma wabu Abandu bandi."
  23,43,"Ne kubulao omukanda kunyala okhuranjilisia indukho yakwo nohomba okhusitia imbeli."
  23,44,"Mana nikhuruma Abarumwa befu, mulala inyuma wowundi. Buli omukanda shingala Omurumwa wabu yaboolela, bamuyingasia. Nikhubalondiakho abandi mubo khubandi, mana nikhubakhola okhuba tsingano. Kho lekha bakorere ehale Abandu balasuubilanga tawe."
  23,45,"Mana nikhuruma Musa nende Omusiani wabu Haruni halala nende ebimanyisio biefu, nende ebifune bili habulafu."
  23,46,"Khwabaruma khu Firauni nende Abandu baye abakhongo, halali bo nibelola, ne nibaba Abandu abafuuru."
  23,47,"Nibaboola mbu; “Khusuubile Abandu babili bano balisa shinga efwe, ne Abandu babu ni Abasumba befu?”"
  23,48,"Mana nibabayingasia mana nibaba mubalia abasishibwa."
  23,49,"Ne toto khwahelesia Musa Eshitabu khobanyoole okhulunjikha."
  23,50,"Ne nikhukhola Omwana wa Mariamu nende nyina okhuba eshimanyisio, ne nikhubahelesia amelushilo habundu wachingukha hali nende obwihotselefu nende tsisebele tsia amatsi."
  23,51,"""Enywe Abarumwa, lie ebilibwa ebilayi ne mukhole amalayi. Toto esie endi Omumanyi muno khukamukholanga."
  23,52,"Ne toto omukanda kwenyu kuno ni omukanda mulala, nasi Esie endi Nyasaye wenyu Omulesi, kho muurie.”"
  23,53,"Mana nibabusia hakari wabu likhuwa lino tsimbeka tsikabukhane. Buli omukanda nikusangalila akakwali ninako."
  23,54,"Kho baleshe sa mubukoyani bwabu okhula shinga ebise biula."
  23,55,"Baparanga mbu bilia ebia khubahelesinjia, omwandu nende abana."
  23,56,"Nibio bia khubaranjilisinjia khubulayi, halali abeene shibamanyile tawe."
  23,57,"Toto balia behotselesinjia khulwa okhuria Nyasaye wabu Omulesi."
  23,58,"Nende balia abasuubilanga ebimanyisio bia Nyasaye wabu Omulesi."
  23,59,"Nende balia abalatsokaasinjia Nyasaye wabu Omulesi tawe."
  23,60,"Nende balia barusinjia ebia bahebwa emioyo chiabu nichiririre mbu toto balikalukha ewa Nyasaye wabu Omulesi."
  23,61,"Abo nibo abanguyilanga amakhuwa amalayi, ne nibo bakaranjililanga."
  23,62,"Nafu shikhutukhanga omundu akaalanyala tawe, ne khuli nende eshitabu eshiboolanga katoto, nabo shibalikholelwa obubii tawe."
  23,63,"Halali emioyo chiabu chili mubukoyano nende ako, ne bali nende ebikhole biabakholanga ebilali ebio tawe (ebia Abandu abalayi bakholanga)."
  23,64,"Okhula shinga khwitsa okhutila (nende okhura mushinyasio) balia bali mubwokholo mubo, awo niwo wabalitsa okhulilikana."
  23,65,"“Mulalilikana inyangayino tawe, toto enywe shimulaona okhurulana ninafu tawe."
  23,66,"Toto mwasomelungwa tsinyaali tsianje, halali enywe mwakalukhanga inyuma khubisisilo bienyu."
  23,67,"Nimuyikholera obufuru, nimuyilomalomakhwo eshilo (khu Ikurani) nimulechele."""
  23,68,"Koo, shibaparangakhwo amakhuwa (akayetsa nako Omurumwa Muhammad), nohomba kabetsela akaletsela bapapa babu beyimbeli tawe?"
  23,69,"Nohomba shibamanya Omurumwa wabu tawe, kho nishichila bamuyingasinjia?"
  23,70,"Nohomba baboolanga mbu (Omurumwa uno) ni omulalu? Halali yabetsela khubwatoto, ne abaanji mubo obwatoto bwabasinya."
  23,71,"Ne obwatoto bulondanga obwikombi bwabu, likulu nende eshialo biakhabiyile nende ebilimwo bioosi. Halali khwabarerera ametsulisio kabu, halali bo beretsanga ehale nende ametsulisio kabu."
  23,72,"Nohomba obasabanga omurungo? Halali omurungo kwa Nyasaye wuwo Omulesi nikwo omulayi, ne niye Omukabi omulayi muno umalayo."
  23,73,"Ne toto ewe obalanganga khunjila ingololofu."
  23,74,"Ne toto balia balasuubilanga mwikulu tawe, beretsanga ehale nende injila (ingololofu) eyo."
  23,75,"Ne kata khubabeelanga tsimbabaasi mana khubarusiliaho obutinyu bwabali ninabo, bakhatsililile mubukori bwabu, nibakoyanile."
  23,76,"Ne toto khwabahelesia eshinyasio (eshilulu) halali shibakalushila Nyasaye wabu Omulesi tawe, ne shibehotselesia tawe."
  23,77,"Okhula shingala khwabekulila omuliango kweshinyasio eshilulu, awo niwo Abandu bawesiakho omwoyo muno."
  23,78,"Ne Ye niye owabalonjela tsimbulililo nende tsindolelo nende emioyo, ne hatiti muno okhupa orio khwenyu."
  23,79,"Naye niye owabaswania khushialo, ne ni ewuwe wamulikhung’asibwa."
  23,80,"Ye niye uhelesinjia obulamu khandi niye ufwisinjia, ne amakalukhano keshilo nende eshitere ni akeke. Koo, shimuparangakhwo tawe?"
  23,81,"Halali baboolanga shingala Abandu bali imbeli baboolanga."
  23,82,"Baboolanga mbu; “Koo, olwa khuliba nikhufwile mana khube liloba nende ebikumba, mbu khokhulilamusibwa?"
  23,83,"Toto khwalakwa kano nende bapapa befu bakhale. Kano ni tsingano tsiakhale butswa."""
  23,84,"Boola mbu; “Liloba nende ebilimwo bioosi ni bia wina toto nikali mbu mumanyile?”"
  23,85,"Balaboola mbu; “Ni bia Nyasaye.” Boola mbu: “Koo, shimwitsulilangakhwo tawe?”"
  23,86,"Boola mbu, ""Ni wina Omwami Omulesi wamakulu saba nende Omulesi weshisaala shiobwami eshikhongo?"""
  23,87,"Balaboola mbu; “Ni bia Nyasaye.” Boola mbu; “Kho koo, shimuritsanga tawe?”"
  23,88,"Boola mbu; “Ni wina womumukhono kukwe bulimwo obwami bwa buli eshindu, naye niye ulindanga, ne sishilindungwa eshia alenyele tawe, toto nimumanyile (mumbolelekhwo)?"""
  23,89,"Balaboola mbu: “Obunyali obo nibwa Nyasaye.” Boola mbu; “Kho mukatibungwa murie?”"
  23,90,"Kho, khubarerere obwatoto halali toto abo ni ababeyi."
  23,91,"Nyasaye abula Omwana yesiyesi, nohomba abulao nyasaye wundi halala ninaye tawe. Kabetsanga kario, buli nyasaye yakhabukule eshiayaloonga, ne abandi mubo bakhashilile abandi. Toto Nyasaye ali ehale nende okhufumia khwabamufuminjia okho."
  23,92,"Omumanyi wakalia kefisile nende akali habulafu, ne ali hekulu muno wa akabamutsokasinjia halala ninaye."
  23,93,"Boola mbu; “Nyasaye wanje Omulesi, ni unzechesia eshinyasio shiabalakungwa."
  23,94,"Nyasaye wanje Omulesi, olaasaasia halala nende Abandu ababii abo tawe."""
  23,95,"Ne toto Efwe khuli noobunyali bwokhukhwechesia akakhwabalaka."
  23,96,"Ikalila amabii khukhukhola amalayi, efwe khumanyile muno akababoolanga."
  23,97,"Ne boola mbu; “Nyasaye wanje Omulesi, ndilinda khwiwe okhurulana nende eshibeyibeyi shia Mashetani."
  23,98,"Ne ndiliinda khwiwe Nyasaye wanje Omulesi kalasitakhwo tawe."""
  23,99,"Okhuula olwa lifwa liulila mulala wabu, aboola mbu; “Nyasaye wanje Omulesi, ngalusia khushialo."
  23,100,"Khenyoole okhukhola amalayi kandalekha."" (Abamalaika balimukalusia mbu); “Shikanyalika tawe,” ni likhuwa butswa lialomalomanga ye mwene. Ne imbeli wabu buliwo obulamu bwemakombe okhula inyanga yokhulamusibwa."
  23,101,"Olwa olwika lulifurwamwo, awo olwikho shilulibaho inyanga eyo tawe, ne shibalireebana tawe."
  23,102,"Kho balia abamalayi kabu kaliba amasiro, abo nibo balibura."
  23,103,"Ne balia abamalayi kabu kaliba amangu, abo betibia abeene, ne baliikhala mumulilo tsinyanga tsioosi."
  23,104,"Omulilo kulinyibulula obweni bwabu, mana bayiniye elwani emino chibulakhwo inyama nibasinyishe muno."
  23,105,"Koo, shimwasomelungwa ta tsinyali tsianje nanyu nimutsiyingasia?"
  23,106,"Baliboola mbu; “Nyasaye wefu Omulesi, obubii bwefu bwakhuyinga muno, mana nikhuba abandu abakori."
  23,107,"Nyasaye wefu Omulesi, khurusie mumulilo kuno (okhukalusie khushialo khukhole amalayi), ne nikhukalulishila khandi, khulaba ababii."""
  23,108,"Aliboola mbu; “Nyiremwo tsi! Ne mulalomalomia tawe.”"
  23,109,"Toto omukanda kwaliwo kwabasumba banje kwaboolanga mbu; “Nyasaye wefu Omulesi, khusuubile, kho khuleshele ebionono biefu ne okhubeele tsimbabaasi. Nawe newe Owetsimbabaasi okhushila boosi.”"
  23,110,"Mana nimubakholela amachayo, mana okhula shinga babakoyania okhunzitsulila, ne mwabatsekhanga."
  23,111,"Toto Esie ebarunjile inyanga yino khulwa okhwifwila khwabu. Toto abo nibo abalibura."
  23,112,"Aliboola mbu; “Mwekhala ebise biyela birie khushialo, khukhubala khwemika?”"
  23,113,"Baliboola mbu; “Khwekhalamwo inyanga ndala nohomba ebise muyinyanga, kho reba balia ababalanga.”"
  23,114,"Aliboola mbu; “Enywe shimwekhalamwo tawe halali ebise bititi butswa, toto mumanyangakhwo sa!"
  23,115,"Koo, muparanga mbu khwabaloonga eshikhaya butswa, ne mbu enywe shimulikalusibwa khwifwe tawe?"
  23,116,"Niwoluyali Nyasaye Omwami watoto, abulaho ulaamungwa khubwatoto halali Ye, Nyasaye weshisaala shiobwami shioluyali."
  23,117,"Ne ulia ulaamanga halala nende Nyasaye nyasaye wundi, ye abula eshifune okhukhola ario, ne toto okhubalilwa ebikhole bibie khuli khu Nyasaye wuwe Omulesi. Ne toto abakhayi shibalibura tawe."
  23,118,"Ne boola mbu; “Nyasaye wanje Omulesi, ndeshela ne umbeele tsimbabaasi. Newe toto omulayi muno wababeeli, Owetsimbabaasi muno."""
